{"database_schema": ""Description for table: LiquidityDeposit"
type LiquidityDeposit implements Event @entity(immutable: true) @transaction {
  "Unique identifier for the liquidity deposit event."
  id: Bytes!
  "Transaction hash associated with the liquidity deposit."
  hash: Bytes!
  "Index of the log entry in the block."
  logIndex: Int!
  "Protocol used for the bridge operation."
  protocol: BridgeProtocol!
  "Account involved in the liquidity deposit."
  account: Account!
  "Destination address for the liquidity deposit."
  to: Bytes!
  "Source address from which the liquidity is deposited."
  from: Bytes!
  "Pool associated with the liquidity deposit."
  pool: Pool!
  "Token involved in the liquidity deposit."
  token: Token!
  "Amount of tokens deposited."
  amount: BigInt!
  "Equivalent amount in USD for the deposited tokens."
  amountUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Identifier for the blockchain network."
  chainID: BigInt!
  "Block number in which the transaction was included."
  blockNumber: BigInt!
  "Timestamp of when the transaction occurred."
  timestamp: BigInt!
}"}
